<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>




<head>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="style.css">
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.1.min.js" integrity="sha256-FgpCb/KJQlLNfOu91ta32o/NMZxltwRo8QtmkMRdAu8=" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="script.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
</head>




<body>




    <div class="hero">

        
        <div class="wrapper">


            <div class="header">
                <a href="https://www.google.com"><div class="mattr-text-logo float-left"><img src="assets/mattr.png"></div></a>
                <div class="header__right">
                    <a href="https://www.google.com"><div class="header__right--signin float-right">SIGN IN</div></a>
                    <a href="https://www.google.com"><div class="header__right--blog float-right">BLOG</div></a>
                </div>
            </div> <!-- /header -->


            <div class="intro">

                <div class="mattr-logo"><img src="assets/mattr-logo.png"></div>

                <div class="intro__text__top">
                    <div class="intro__text--large">Personalities</div>
                    <div class="intro__text--large">tell powerful stories.</div>
                </div>

                <div class="intro__text__center">
                    <div class="intro__text--small">The key to successful brand engagement lies within the vibrant</div>
                    <div class="intro__text--small">personalities that make up online audiences. Mattr translates the social</div>
                    <div class="intro__text--small">data they generate into powerful stories and actionable insights,</div>
                    <div class="intro__text--small">allowing brands to connect on a deeper level with their targets.</div>
                </div>

                <div class="intro__text__bottom">
                    <div class="intro__text--medium">GET TO KNOW YOUR AUDIENCE.</div>
                    <div class="intro__text--medium">REQUEST A PRIVATE BETA INVITATION:</div>
                </div>

                <div class="invite">
                    <input class="email__field" type="email" placeholder="your@email.com">
                    <div class="invite__request float-right">
                        <a href="https://www.google.com" class="invite__request--text">REQUEST INVITE</a>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div> <!-- /intro -->


        </div> <!-- /wrapper -->


    </div> <!-- /hero -->


    <div class="content">


        <div class="block the-app">
            <h>The App</h>
            <p>Mattr allows you to build a more complete view of your social media audience through a comprehensive set of segmentation, comparison, monitoring, and visualization tools.  Explore our Features to learn more.</p>
        </div>


        <div class="block audience feature">
            <div class="image">
                <img class="image__icon" src="assets/audience.svg">
                <img class="image__btn" src="assets/plus.png">
            </div>
            <h>Audience Personality Segments</h>
            <p>Decide how you want to look at your audience, based on our Unique Personality Type Analysis and demographics.</p>
        </div>


        <div class="block persona feature">
            <div class="image">
                <img class="image__icon" src="assets/persona.png">
                <img class="image__btn" src="assets/plus.png">
            </div>
            <h>Persona Builder</h>
            <p>Combine Personality Traits and Demographic information to create Audience Personas that make sense for your business.</p>
        </div>


        <div class="block engagement feature">
            <div class="image">
                <img class="image__icon" src="assets/engagement.png">
                <img class="image__btn" src="assets/plus.png">
            </div>
            <h>Engagement Response by Persona</h>
            <p>Which of your social media activities are attracting the audience engagement you're looking for? See a segmented report on a per-post basis.</p>
        </div>


        <div class="block social feature">
            <div class="image">
                <img class="image__icon" src="assets/social.png">
                <img class="image__btn" src="assets/plus.png">
            </div>
            <h>Engagement Response by Persona</h>
            <p>Which of your social media activities are attracting the audience engagement you're looking for? See a segmented report on a per-post basis.</p>
        </div>


        <div class="block sentiment feature">
            <div class="image">
                <img class="image__icon" src="assets/sentiment.png">
                <img class="image__btn" src="assets/plus.png">
            </div>
            <h>Engagement Response by Persona</h>
            <p>Which of your social media activities are attracting the audience engagement you're looking for? See a segmented report on a per-post basis.</p>
        </div>


    </div>




